    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、琴乃さんだー！　琴乃さ～～～～ん！\nえいっ！",
      "startTime": 7.3666668098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "わあっ！？\nえっ、す、すみれ？　びっくりした……",
      "startTime": 9.0000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、すみません！　クリスマスだからかな\nなんだかわくわくしちゃって。えへへ",
      "startTime": 17.3333335241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの番組、休憩中に観てましたよ！\nそのヘアアレンジも、すっごく可愛いです！",
      "startTime": 23.9000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。すみれも、同じ局でお仕事だったんだ？\n瑠依さんと、優は？",
      "startTime": 32.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "二人は、まだ他にお仕事があるみたいで\nだからちょうど良かったです。一緒に帰りましょう！",
      "startTime": 37.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。みんな、パーティーの準備があるからって\n先に帰っちゃったのよね。待っててくれてもいいのに",
      "startTime": 45.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7199.999999999995,
          "startTime": 52.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15766.666666599995,
          "startTime": 61.3333333333
        },
