      "text": "わ、クリスマスだからかな。人が多いわね……\nすみれ、はぐれないように…………あ……",
      "startTime": 59.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です、琴乃さんの袖、ぎゅってしてますから\nイルミネーション、綺麗ですね～",
      "startTime": 68.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "（……か、可愛い。あんまりこういう風に）\n（甘えられたことなかったから……なんか新鮮）",
      "startTime": 75.4666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、お姉ちゃんと手繋ごっか",
      "startTime": 80.0666678984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、はい。じゃあ……\n繋ぎましょう、琴乃お姉ちゃん",
      "startTime": 89.0666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（私がお姉ちゃん……）\n（……お姉ちゃんも、こんな気持ちだったのかな）",
      "startTime": 94.8333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "…………っ！\nあれ……今…………なんだか…………",
      "startTime": 100.4999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃さん？　どうかしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 107.9333203236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……クリスマス、だから……？\n私も、わくわくして、そわそわして……胸が熱くて……",
      "startTime": 114.4666488647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
