      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あの子のことだから、向こうでもライブしてるだろうし",
      "startTime": 123.7999874989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれ、ダッシュで帰ろっか\nなんだか、みんなの顔が早く見たくなってきちゃった",
      "startTime": 132.399982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-01-night"
    },
    {
